{"ja259:0.1":"Jataka ","ja259:0.2":"Tikanipata ","ja259:0.3":"Sankappavagga ","ja259:0.4":"9. Tiritavacchajataka ","ja259:1.1":"“Nayimassa vijjamayamatthi kinci, ","ja259:1.2":"Na bandhavo no pana te sahayo; ","ja259:1.3":"Atha kena vannena tiritavaccho, ","ja259:1.4":"Tedandiko bhunjati aggapindam”. ","ja259:2.1":"“Apasu me yuddhaparajitassa, ","ja259:2.2":"Ekassa katva vivanasmi ghore; ","ja259:2.3":"Pasarayi kicchagatassa panim, ","ja259:2.4":"Tenudatarim dukhasampareto. ","ja259:3.1":"Etassa kiccena idhanupatto, ","ja259:3.2":"Vesayino visaya jivaloke; ","ja259:3.3":"Labharaho tata tiritavaccho, ","ja259:3.4":"Dethassa bhogam yajathanca yannan”ti. ","ja259:4.1":"Tiritavacchajatakam navamam. "}